Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:18.43,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The next day, Chizu-chan came to school looking refreshed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.03,0:01:22.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,as if she'd finally pulled a splinter out of her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:27.87,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She still wouldn't talk to Sanada-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:31.39,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but she didn't seem to be ignoring him like yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:37.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:39.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:42.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in, as long as it's not an all-you-can-eat or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.97,0:01:44.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:44.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:49.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:57.02,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like Chizu-chan had come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:03.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last time we sang was at the sports day party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:06.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'm as pissed at Ryu as I was anymore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:08.69,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to have ramen before we go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At Sanada-kun's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:15.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:18.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I think I might get pissed again if I look at his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:19.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:24.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We said a lot about Ryu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:29.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm actually glad he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:34.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might not have been able to snap if he weren't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:41.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking, ever since that fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:47.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have wanted to talk to Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:52.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:57.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I could have talked to him the way I was, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:00.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you say when you next see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:01.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“I love you.”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:04.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:08.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't think I was serious, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:10.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, that's really not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.69,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:16.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:19.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know what he'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:25.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:27.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:31.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:32.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:44.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm borrowing Chi for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:48.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:50.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:53.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:57.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your miniskirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:15.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:28.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she'll be able to say what she wants to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:48.38,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she'll be at peace next time they meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:54.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go for tea or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:56.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:02.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you staying the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:10.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm going home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:14.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked hard today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:17.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to finish early so I could come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And more work tomorrow morning already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:23.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you don't get home until midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:30.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the boring talk, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:36.21,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:47.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:55.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:58.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? I'm wearing a miniskirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:05.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you've always liked showing off your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:10.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tireless as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:12.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an old fart now, it's too cold for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:15.64,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, he's used to seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:18.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not an old fart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:23.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,24 must seem old at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:28.89,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's treating me even more like a kid than he would otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.95,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste of a nice pair of legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.46,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:40.60,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My poor thighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:46.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, where's your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:49.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:54.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I didn't have a car when I used to hang out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd walk with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, a meat bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:15.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a bean paste bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:21.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to eat this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:28.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A meat bun, or a bean paste bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A meat bun, or a bean paste bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:32.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:36.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll want savory stuff after sweet stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:38.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll run out of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:43.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mom will kill me if I eat two and spoil dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want both.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A meat bun, or a bean paste bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:51.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A meat bun, or a bean paste bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:54.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of each, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:00.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have half.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:08.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:20.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could have handled two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:41.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That street lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:48.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to come down this street when I was out at night during high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:52.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'd often be a kid under that lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:58.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would there be kids outside so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:01.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the horror story all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:03.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be hunting for stag beetles,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:06.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at three in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:10.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That scared me so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to wake up so early when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:19.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we used to walk home together,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,looking at the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:29.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which star is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but it's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:36.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huge star.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:39.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only know about Orion's Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:40.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orion's Belt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:43.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:43.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:45.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Orion's Belt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:50.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a triplet of stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:52.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the triplet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:00.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was a winter constellation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky's so dark in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:13.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:16.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:26.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Chizu said what she wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:30.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:34.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you like someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:39.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sad things, things that make you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:44.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a lot of happy things too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:11:02.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember? How you tripped over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how we used to eat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:11.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru was always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:14.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to come down this street a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:20.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:24.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ryu's running course now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:26.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that field.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:29.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place Ryu made you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure do remember a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:35.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he still make you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:37.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:41.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}I hate Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:45.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he doesn't make me cry. He doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:47.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:53.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lash out at him sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:59.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu's nice, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't lie either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:08.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are close together,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess it hurts when he says things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:15.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it wouldn't have hurt if someone else had said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:23.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you get in that kind of fight with Ryu now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:30.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look good in your uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:37.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in high school now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:44.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:47.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd never settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you decide to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:04.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I wanted to be with her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:10.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So did I, ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:15.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed like a mellow, cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:20.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's actually pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:25.04,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how much he cared for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.13,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,or how many memories we made together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.28,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Or even that I'm in high school now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,A kid from the block is still a kid from the block.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:48.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why I call you Chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:49.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:09.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:16.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:17.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:19.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:55.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.11,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:07.89,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:12.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It still makes me happy though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:19.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm not a sister or relative or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:21.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a kid from the block.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:27.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can I come visit you next time you're back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:30.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound so depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think of you as a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe even cuter than Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell Ryu though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:47.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:54.30,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be a different person in front of his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:57.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:01.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that you think highly of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:07.72,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,As my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:14.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:24.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:36.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, out for a run?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:38.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Chizuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:42.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I walked her home, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heading home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:47.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so proper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:56.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:17:00.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should be fine, it's winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:02.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:05.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten huge too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:07.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be taller than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:10.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will, I'm in my growth spurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:17.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of you are exactly smooth talkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:20.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:23.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a better match for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:25.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:30.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:38.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys will be boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:42.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:46.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you with Chizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.49,0:17:50.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so late, I thought she'd be at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:54.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could that silly girl be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:58.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Ryu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:05.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a girl after all, believe it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to cheer you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:30.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to be nice to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you trying to start a fight? Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:35.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:44.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we last hung out when my brother lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:50.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were here when he moved to Sapporo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:56.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you not to talk to me for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:58.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shut up, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:08.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:09.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:15.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was your birthday that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:16.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:22.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the only one that was there to celebrate this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:24.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:30.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you were the only one who remembered my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the pouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:39.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called Tohru over, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:43.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him if he was hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:45.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said you'd given him some bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:51.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not shocked or anything though, just because you called him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:54.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He spent three and a half hours to come here, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:57.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:05.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:11.02,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That I was hopelessly in love with Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:17.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I never really thought it would work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:22.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he was just an older brother that I admired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:31.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you really liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:50.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comfort me, Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:17.79,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the first snow of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:32.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The holy night,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.84,0:22:35.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with wishes deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:38.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:41.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
